  27,49,"They said: "
  27,50,"So they plotted a plot, and We plotted a plot, while they perceived not."
  27,51,"Then see how was the end of their plot! Verily! We destroyed them and their nation, all together."
  28,22,"And when he went towards (the land of) Madyan (Midian), he said: "
  28,23,"And when he arrived at the water (a well) of Madyan (Midian) he found there a group of men watering (their flocks), and besides them he found two women who were keeping back (their flocks). He said: "
  28,24,"So he watered (their flocks) for them, then he turned back to shade, and said: "